Package common

Class Test

  • java.lang.Object
    • common.Test
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Test
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents a Test object. The Test class implements the Serializable interface, allowing objects of this class to be serialized and deserialized. It contains fields to store various properties of a test, such as select, ID, subject text, course name, author text, status, duration, and test code.
